				\begin{document}$$\{y_\mu ,y_\nu \}$$\end{document} of Eq. (3.11), which is linear in the coordinates. Note that in the case of an open string moving in the flat background coordinate is linear function in both effective momenta and coordinates. Therefore, the corresponding PB is constant.

